org.apache.hadoop.hive.metastore.model

Class MPartitionColumnStatistics

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hive.metastore.model.MPartitionColumnStatistics

  • public class MPartitionColumnStatistics
extends Object
    MPartitionColumnStatistics - Represents Hive's partiton level Column Statistics Description. The fields in this class with the exception of partition are persisted in the metastore. In case of partition, part_id is persisted in its place.
